Recommendations
Short-term Improvements

Add input validation and error handling
Implement data persistence (database/file storage)
Enhance inventory management features
Add user authentication and authorization

Long-term Enhancements

Develop a more sophisticated prediction algorithm
Add reporting and analytics features
Implement a graphical user interface
Add transaction management and logging
Implement proper security measures

Conclusion
The system provides a solid foundation for basic ERP functionality. While currently limited in scope, its modular design allows for easy expansion. The code structure is clean and well-organized, making it maintainable and extensible. Implementation of the recommended improvements would significantly enhance its utility and robustness.
